# Make Private key
```
openssl genrsa -out private_key.pem 2048
```

# Make Public key
```
openssl rsa -in private_key.pem -outform PEM -pubout -out public_key.pem
```


# Sign File by public key

## Signing:
```
openssl dgst -sha256 ROZP_13980919_01_OK.txt > hash
openssl rsautl -sign -inkey private_key.pem -keyform PEM -in hash >signature
```

## Verifying just the signature:
```
openssl rsautl -verify -inkey public_key.pem -pubin -keyform PEM -in signature
```



## Verifying that the owner of the private key does vouch for ROZP_13980919_01_OK.txt:

```
openssl dgst -sha256 -verify public_key.pem -signature signature ROZP_13980919_01_OK.txt
```